{
  "stem": "1343.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what is horrible-- and, again, we used to scream to God that how come that I am suffering from nightmares and these murderers living out long life, raising families, going to church and whatnot, and they have no conscience.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there is no such a thing, it seems like, the conscience, either.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We started to hear a few days earlier, already, cannoning, canon fire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the next day, we heard already the heavy weapons, like machine guns.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then after that we heard guns.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew that something is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one afternoon, the SS guard disappeared.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When that happened, like a crazy hoard, there were still some 12-- more than 10,000 people, for sure, in that camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they all ran for the magazines, for the supply.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not the ammunition.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where the food was kept.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was carried along, and actually, it was downstairs, the house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they opened the door-- when the doors were already open, they swept me, and then all of a sudden, boom.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I fell down, and a bunch of people on top of me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So at first, I thought I'd suffocate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, there, we found some bread, some mayonnaise and fat, pork fat, on top of it.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
